Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面要读哪本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间大量的推理小说完好无损地漂流到了岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实有件事我一直想做做看  哪怕就一次也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  就是像推理小说中的主人公那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想试着真正去和怪人决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去解决事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想以此为蓝本来写小说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是清正先生的话应该能写好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.65,0:00:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定写一下试试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会期待着的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没有文采的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:24.93,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去揭秘吧  侦探（后篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之名为红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话那邀请帖果然是你发的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绫音所看到的我  也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.74,0:02:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  百面怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想听到年轻少女的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看到她们恐怖的表情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在那少女的皮肤上涂了岛上最痒的东部森林的山药汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然会自然好转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过得要一周时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想立刻就治好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使用这解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点把那个拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…居然对我重要的客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你作为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行排除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐  稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要解毒药的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在满月还未消失之前抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么做的话  就全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  不能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是朔夜小姐把什么当作敌人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐照顾周到特意为我们放的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边洗澡一边看烟花也是很享受的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是红夜叉但也是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像被逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躲开我的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是敌人但也值得钦佩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  先回月见亭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为事件会就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人好迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要泡到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得大家都住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天马上就要过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的乐趣现在才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是马上要睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃真是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上不单单只是睡觉的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整晚努力的修行也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那凛到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带行人大人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他睡在同一被窝里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一整晚在里面卿卿我我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是睡觉技能的特训吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忍  我觉得不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  大姐头不能偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想…想和公子…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃也想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说很大胆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  行人和我同一个房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起睡的应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃不是每晚都睡一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  让我们一晚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在还没出嫁之前女孩子怎么就能做出这样的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还是未成年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话真是没完没了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里轮到我出场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你浅薄的智慧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正起不到什么作用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  在行人洗澡回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先回自己的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后只剩下给行人的信而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信…要写什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想与你一起共渡良宵  请来我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  让行人自己来选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是挑战书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也许行人会谁都不选独自一人去空房间睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让它们去空房间待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等行人来了把他赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人最喜欢的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切将在今晚揭晓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人…最喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么  当然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  也许是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛才不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照其行动规律来看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会假扮成某人然后混到大家里面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窥视等待引发下次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么的话  请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否是假货  我会识破他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  真不愧是科学的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么特殊的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  只是想一个一个扯她们的脸来确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐要是去扯的话  就算是真的皮肤也会扯掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜小姐伤害了客人  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么原始的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有更加科学性的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据红外线透视
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据声纹和体温的个体识别之类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有那么便利的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是SF
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(SF：Science  Fiction  超现实的作品)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为朔夜小姐的存在本身已经是SF了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里不能依靠科学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠直接的方法来把他逼到绝境了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  对侦探来说最大的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是顶头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(顶头：相扑和摔跤的格斗手段之一，用自己的头部顶向对手进行攻击)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用头脑  也就是推理力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着吧  红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受这挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来…不会来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是练习  练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不能在公子面前太随意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也得稍微注重下仪表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  怎么还不来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了的话玩什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  已经看过信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的人所在的地方  会是谁的房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是宫本武藏打倒佐佐木小次郎时的战法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁心智混乱之时忽然闪现一口气决出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会上当
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了尖叫  过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍小姐  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师…傅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是因为激烈的按摩而动弹不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么按摩会那么激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来曾有什么人在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类按摩椅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是谁会做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是红夜叉  千影小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了  真正的红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那邀请帖是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才绫音牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍就是第二个牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去  就会出现第三  第四个牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再让你擅自妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和行人单独两人渡过一夜的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会这样扑过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后奇痒无比  难过死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手却够不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  再下面点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音皮肤真美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是因为太痒而进入了妄想世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也许会稍微轻松点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红夜叉那家伙接下来打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新的牺牲者出现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点阻止的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梅梅小姐的尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么沾在脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道又是山药汁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  身体有什么地方痒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…梅梅你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…虽然还不值得夸耀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  忽然怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是平常害羞的梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:34.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让行人大人看到害羞的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那孩子所涂的不是山药汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那孩子涂的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦沾到便会立即想做H的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘑菇泥汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然解毒药在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看来少年也不是不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅拜托你们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:13:59.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经睡着了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫醒有点过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不使用这发笑的药了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回不让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错  就是这个状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  刚才开始就那么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  尿床了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个敏捷的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  是凛的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么回来这里  命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为姐姐不带我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  你选择我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那像大叔一样的毫无疑问是真正的命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那样的话只能一个个找了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没理由就被打出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红夜叉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来梅梅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔夜这样打了她一下就让她睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才上面有可疑的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  在二楼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特大红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  还醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红夜叉出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是看了信而过来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我放心了  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我最喜欢的人是小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等  行人你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧  怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那给你看证据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才所说的红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃的话  能分清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟每天都一起生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个行人  和平常的感觉有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  仔细看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我适可而止  离开小铃身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀…杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…这时候一般应该互相证明自己是真的才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁理你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点玩过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让你逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经穷途末路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在小说里不清楚你是谁就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我会在这里揭穿你的真实面目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没有注意到被引诱上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有恐高症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然怕的动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前邀请来的男人还能再稍微有点乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对做不到像那个男人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许…说绝对做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  解毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要落下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如传言中那样是个很有趣的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得那孩子会如此中意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得涌出了创作欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…总有一天会在满月之时再会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能让他跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭那么点洞察力就像揭穿我的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早得很
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他不服输的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面时还是小心点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时是会使用忍者招术的怪人红夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时以那事件为基础而写小说神秘的作家静丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过其真实身份是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千影  辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这试炼如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如千影所说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合第二代主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人期待的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然怪人的宿敌就该是拥有强烈的不服输精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那比什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能看到静丸的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上的读者都会非常高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过无论怎么说  已经约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会再次写新作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和静丸最重要的书迷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演红夜叉并开始写小说的契机是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了引起那位喜欢推理小说的书迷的注意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  我会害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经早上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:21:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是不知道行人选择了谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉是有点遗憾却又松了一口气的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  我们噩梦般的一晚结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  红夜叉的牺牲者太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红夜叉  这愤怒总有一天会偿还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  要揭穿你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:11.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月见亭的杀人事件
